examples.translation: He had brutally murdered his daughter.

examples.text: Sen bir daha şarkı söyleme, şarkıyı katlettin resmen.
examples.translation: Don't ever sing again, you just murdered the song.

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish قتل ایتمك (katl etmek). By surface analysis, katil (“murder”) + etmek (“to make, to do”).
